OL,3,CNI primary healthcare sector in
OL,4,C'crisis'
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's primary care sector
OL,7,Fis in crisis and urgently needs
OL,8,Fradical reform, according to a new
OL,9,Freport from Stormont's Public Accounts
OL,10,FCommittee (PAC).
OL,12,FThe report, Access to General Practice
OL,13,Fin Northern Ireland, highlights
OL,14,Fserious failings in how patients
OL,15,Faccess GP services and sets out ten
OL,16,Frecommendations for change.
