OL,6,FThe committee received evidence from
OL,7,Fthe British Medical Association NI,
OL,8,Fthe Royal College of General
OL,9,FPractitioners, the Patient and Client
OL,10,FCouncil and the Department of Health.
OL,12,FIt also ran its own public call for
OL,13,Fevidence, receiving more than 15,000
OL,14,Fresponses. Over half of respondents
OL,15,Frated their experience of contacting
OL,16,Ftheir GP practice as "poor", with many
OL,17,Freporting repeated failed attempts and
OL,18,Fincreased stress, anxiety and
OL,19,Ffinancial strain.
