OL,6,FCommittee chair Daniel McCrossan said
OL,7,Fpatients were being let down by a
OL,8,Fsystem that is "a cornerstone of basic
OL,9,Fmedical care".
OL,11,F"It beggars belief that some of the
OL,12,Ffundamental building blocks of primary
OL,13,Fcare are not in place," he said.
OL,26,@pD@POUqD@MO]sD@AOUuD@WO]
