OL,3,CNI primary healthcare sector in
OL,4,C'crisis'
OL,6,FHe added that GP workload pressures,
OL,7,Fincluding knock-on effects from
OL,8,Fhospital demand, were contributing to
OL,9,Fa system under severe strain. The
OL,10,FCommittee heard evidence that patients
OL,11,Fin Northern Ireland see a GP on
OL,12,Faverage nine times a year ` three
OL,13,Ftimes the level in the Republic.
OL,15,FThe Department of Health told the
OL,16,FCommittee it was "too difficult" to
OL,17,Fmeasure demand for GP services and
OL,18,Fconfirmed it does not hold figures on
OL,19,Fhow many full-time equivalent GPs are
OL,20,Fcurrently working in Northern Ireland.
OL,26,@xD@ROUxD@`O]
