OL,3,CNI primary healthcare sector in
OL,4,C'crisis'
OL,6,FThe committee also found there is no
OL,7,Fprimary care workforce strategy,
OL,8,Fsomething it warns has significant
OL,9,Fconsequences for recruitment and long-
OL,10,Fterm planning.
OL,12,FMcCrossan described as "shocking"
OL,13,Fevidence that some GP partners have
OL,14,Fhanded back contracts only to be
OL,15,Frehired immediately as locum doctors
OL,16,Fat higher cost.
OL,18,F"This is an inappropriate practice and
OL,19,Fan unacceptable way of using public
OL,20,Fmoney," he said.
