OL,3,CNI primary healthcare sector in
OL,4,C'crisis'
OL,6,FPAC Deputy Chair Diane Forsythe said
OL,7,Fimproving access depended on stronger
OL,8,Fworking relationships between the
OL,9,FDepartment of Health and GPs.
OL,11,F"Everyone involved must work together
OL,12,Fto deliver better outcomes for those
OL,13,Fin need," she said.
OL,15,FThe committee called for a full
OL,16,Fprimary care strategy within a year,
OL,17,Fincluding a dedicated workforce plan
OL,18,Fand clearer direction for future
OL,19,Fservices.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@IO]
