OL,3,CNI primary healthcare sector in
OL,4,C'crisis'
OL,6,FMs Forsythe said the department needed
OL,7,Fto better capture the "patient's
OL,8,Fvoice", noting a significant
OL,9,Fdisconnect between complaints recorded
OL,10,Fby the Patient and Client Council `
OL,11,Fwhich reported a 70% rise in
OL,12,Fcomplaints ` and the department's own
OL,13,Ffigures, which suggested a fall.
OL,15,FDigitisation was also highlighted as a
OL,16,Fpriority. The committee said the
OL,17,Fintroduction of e-prescribing could
OL,18,Fease pressure on practices and improve
OL,19,Fefficiency, and has urged the
OL,20,Fdepartment to complete a business case
OL,21,Fwithin six months.
OL,26,@oD@WOUpD@FO]
