OL,6,FAmong the committee's 10
OL,7,Frecommendations is a call for a public
OL,8,Feducation programme within the next 12
OL,9,Fmonths, helping people understand the
OL,10,Fmost appropriate routes for care `
OL,11,Fwhether through GP practices,
OL,12,Fpharmacies, minor injuries units or
OL,13,Femergency departments.
OL,15,FThe committee also wants improved data
OL,16,Fon patient experience, including
OL,17,Fcomplaints, to be shared and used to
OL,18,Fdrive change.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
