OL,6,FMs Forsythe said that while some
OL,7,Fprogress had been made in developing
OL,8,Fnew primary care models, it remained
OL,9,F"slow and small scale."
OL,11,F"To safeguard services and build for
OL,12,Fthe future, the department must be
OL,13,Fmore proactive in leading the
OL,14,Fconversation on future delivery
OL,15,Fmodels," she added.
